items.title: Senco Gold Limited: Shining growth prospects
items.description: SGL is accelerating its network reach to strengthen presence in the jewellery industry. The ramp-up of lab-grown diamonds (LGDs) and fashion accessories remains an additional growth trigger.

items.title: JSW Group Chairman Sajjan Jindal plans to indigenise electric vehicle technology, set up R&D centres
items.description: The group, through its joint venture company JSW MG Motor India, entered the electric vehicle space earlier this year and currently relies on the Chinese company for technology.

items.title: Jeff Bezos is betting on AI chip startup Tenstorrent to take on Nvidia
items.description: Tenstorrent is also a proponent of an alternative kind of logic processor based on an open standard called RISC-V, which poses a challenge to Arm Holdings Plc.
